tool_description: Restful API to query definitions and examples of math concepts
name: Mathionary
title: Mathionary

api_list.name: basic
api_list.description: Query basic math concepts and examples.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://mathionary.p.rapidapi.com/basic"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "mathionary.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
